data: Telekinesis is not just your ordinary gaming event. It's a mind-bending experience where you get to play the game using only the power of your mind! With the help of an EEG headband-powered Brain-Computer Interface, you'll tap into your brain's potential and unleash your telekinetic abilities to play games like Brain Breakout, Mind Pong, and many more. Simply put on the EEG headband, focus your mind, and watch as your thoughts translate into actions on the screen. No controllers are needed - just your brainpower! Plus, each game session lasts for 10 minutes, giving you plenty of time to test your telekinetic skills.
Unlock the Power of Your Mind: Game Beyond Limits!
